title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-05-2013 THURS
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-05-2013 THURS








Thursday, December 05, 2013


Fast Food Protests, Liberalism In Hollywood, And Adam 12 Shool Board ElectioN
 
 

 - 9AM hour

Kenric Ward with Watchdog.org joins Mike this morning to discuss the protests today

                       at fast food restaurants for a higher pay and a higher minimum wage.




 - 10AM hour

David Mamet joins Mike to talk about his book "Three War Stories" and liberalism
        
                                 in Hollywood and the Jewish community.




 - 11AM hour

Colorado Secretary of State Scott Gessler joins Mike to give us an update
                                             on the Adams 12 School Board Election.
